      "BS EN 13480 Metallic Industrial Piping",
      "SMACNA HVAC Duct Construction Standards 4th ed (ANSI/SMACNA 006-2020)",
      "DW/144 UK Specification for Sheet Metal Ductwork",
      "BS EN 1507 / 12237 Ductwork leakage classification",
      "BESA TR/19 Ductwork cleanliness",
      "NFPA 90A / UL 555 Fire damper rules",
      "BS EN 61386 Conduit systems",
      "BS 7671 Requirements for Electrical Installations §522/527",
      "BS EN 61537 Cable tray / ladder systems",
      "BS EN 50174-2 Information technology cabling — installation",
